casebody.data:
Frankie Jae LORDMASTER, fka Jason Robert Goldader, petitioner,
v.
Harold W. CLARKE, Director, Virginia Department of Corrections, et al. No. 16-7780. Supreme Court of the United States April 17, 2017.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Virginia dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
